.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站              <br />\n   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=2a6f7cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"5576669bf0c8d6ba8031ac7bb2d8d91ea7bdd586","tid":2336901,"uid":138187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"加油 你的家人和朋友都愛你💪🏻"},{"pid":"63f1b6cf506d20e3be05b1b796a7d5a332986134","tid":2336901,"uid":136049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a70c40d28c149aa8634bcecd343e91c256c5ce","tid":2336901,"uid":324123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b9586ea6d26f2cbc4d1e2e7c7750d3808de99c","tid":2336901,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"5a8d8f2cc3c2d96f274144281660d02d1c7e624e","tid":2336901,"uid":32113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2024ae03081964d43e107eee91a67d65fa0d2f26","tid":2336901,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":64,"score":-58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T03:02:47.000Z","msg":"個個都係咁架啦 叫乜撚野春 收嗲啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"早啲屌醒佢 等佢知個世界係咁殘酷<br />\n唔通你想好慘好慘然後圍爐圍一世？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"你見唔見你有好多負評？<br />\n收下把口啦 dllm"},{"pid":"c91de4db06daa339d21c544191c7fbc40ed0b03f","tid":2336901,"uid":12033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T20:58:41.000Z","msg":"我都有<